title: Rossell, Baix Maestrat
text:
Rossell () is a <a href="Municipalities%20of%20Spain">municipality</a> in the <a href="Comarques%20of%20the%20Valencian%20community">"comarca"</a> of <a href="Baix%20Maestrat">Baix Maestrat</a> in the <a href="Valencian%20Community">Valencian Community</a>, Spain.
The town is located at the eastern end of the <a href="Ports%20de%20Tortosa-Beseit">Ports de Tortosa-Beseit</a>, in the area known as <a href="Muntanyes%20de%20Benifass%C3%A0">Muntanyes de Benifassà</a>. Rossell is part of the <a href="Taula%20del%20S%C3%A9nia">Taula del Sénia</a> free association of municipalities.
